      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "vending machine state design patternn\nDocument Editor me - GFG, Medium  Docemt is in edit state, archive state, deleted state, published state\nATM Machine is also used for the State Design Pattern\nAndroid Operating state, tiorun on phone, load the OS, run the OS, Run the star up aps, optimize the bettery and activate background processes\nactivater the network card features, BT, Wifi etc all this are the diffrent states simpe ",
